D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d6/%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg/32px-%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%99%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%95%D7%93%D7%A9_5.svg.png 2x\" /></span></span><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%95%D7%9F_%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%99%D7%9F\" title=\"חב&quot;ד און ליין\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/15px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/23px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/30px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://old2.ih.chabad.info/#!g=1&amp;url=article&amp;id=74630\">המאמץ השמיימי להביא את הגאולה ● מיוחד</a> מתוך העיתון \"שעה טובה\" <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95\" title=\"חב&quot;ד אינפו\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/27px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"9\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/41px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/54px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></li>\n<li>הפגישה עם הבית ישראל ראש בני ישראל עמ' 215.</li></ul>\n<h2><span id=\".D7.94.D7.A2.D7.A8.D7.95.D7.AA_.D7.A9.D7.95.D7.9C.D7.99.D7.99.D7.9D\"></span><span cla